    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but you said it increases the levels in my blood... if the levels get too high isn't that dangerous? like can it cause muscle damage or something? i'm kinda scared to take it if it's going to be toxic. should i just stop the simvastatin until the antibiotics are done so i don't have to worry?",
